body:
Well I have been up for 2 days so far trying to play some ranked games. Around 7 games ago my computer had a blue screen in the middle of the game and as I tried my hardest to reconnect I could not come back (The game lasted 22 mins and my team won without me.(In a normal queue)) so I received 5 games in the low priority queue of a 20 min wait time. I attempted to email riot to get this injustice resolved but I ended up playing 5 games in low priority before they could respond which is 100 minutes of wait time and each game being around 30 minutes as well. So after finally being freed from my unfair low priority prison I played a bunch more games. All of the games I had played up until this point were perfectly fine and I had no issues, until that one match happened. During this one game I got 13000+ ping and could not move, after a long attempt of trying to fix this problem (Shutting down EVERY other thing on my computer but league of legends, restarting computer and restarting my internet.) I eventually gave up and sat at spawn waiting for this ping to go down so I could communicate what was happening to my team with little luck. I never stopped trying but my team had ended the game and won their team was salty and all the usual league of legends community stuff. I still got put in another Low Priority Queue for another (to what I assume is 5 games of 20 minutes each.) I know a lot of you are gonna say stuff like "Don't play ranked if you have a toaster and bad internet" but this was a 1 time thing, people will also probably say "But there is so much toxic feeders and trolls so this way is good even if innocent get punished." I also know that there is no way to really figure out if someone had really disconnected or is just a troll but there has to be a better version than "Hey look they disconnected and didn't move for 3 minutes lets give them 20 minutes of wait time before every game even if they reconnect so they learn their lesson of not playing unless directly connected to the server. In conclusion I know that Riot is not gonna help me or remove this low priority because why should they for all they know I just decided to afk to try to make my teammates lives just a little bit harder so I am not hoping for that, What I am hoping for is that this post reaches out to the group of people who have felt this and have been banned for something beyond their power. I really just want this to go to somewhere where someone will consider this and try to make a way to make this problem better (If you have any ideas share them!) and help out all wrongfully banned summoners in the future!

TL:DR : I got put in low priority for something that I couldn't control and now I'm bitching about it and trying to get something done for myself and others in the future (Share your ideas for a better afk punishing system so we can get somewhere with this!

